PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,FKate Mitchell was found dead in her
OL,8,Fhotel bedroom in Nairobi with head and
OL,9,Fneck injuries. The alleged killer had
OL,10,Fjumped or fell to his death from an
OL,11,Feighth floor balcony.
OL,13,FLast year a Newcastle coroner found
OL,14,Fshe had been unlawfully killed, but
OL,15,Fher brother, Pete still has many
OL,16,Fquestions over how his sister was
OL,17,Fmurdered four-and-a-half years on.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,FHe told ITV News Tyne Tees: "There's
OL,8,Fbeen an inquest in the UK, which had
OL,9,Fto take place with absolute minimal
OL,10,Fdocumentation, because essentially the
OL,11,FKenyan authorities just haven't been
OL,12,Fcommunicating with us. They haven't
OL,13,Fbeen cooperating, and as the inquest
OL,14,Fin Kenya goes on, they've been
OL,15,Fincreasingly obstructive.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,F"So far I've been out to Kenya three
OL,8,Ftimes, each one with a gap of three
OL,9,Fmonths between them, and we get about
OL,10,Ftwo hours in court. This last time we
OL,11,Fonly got one single witness. So
OL,12,Fobviously, if we run that out, then
OL,13,Fthe case will become exhausted.
OL,14,FWitnesses will disappear. One has
OL,15,Falready died, and it just becomes very
OL,16,Fdifficult to achieve anything.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,F"It's really frustrating, yeah.
OL,8,FThere's a sense that the clock is
OL,9,Fbeing run out and that this is an
OL,10,Fattempt to exhaust this. I am going to
OL,11,Fkeep coming back though."
OL,13,FPete is calling for the remaining
OL,14,Fhearings to be held on consecutive
OL,15,Fdays, but he also has a number of
OL,16,Fother concerns about the proceedings.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,FSo far, only a handful of the 23
OL,8,Flisted witnesses have given evidence
OL,9,Fand this month, Pete attended the
OL,10,Fthird hearing hoping to hear evidence
OL,11,Ffrom the country's chief pathologist,
OL,12,Fbut he failed to turn up.
OL,14,FPete added: "There were a lot of
OL,15,Fquestions about those post-mortems,
OL,16,Fjust as there are about the entire
OL,17,Fconduct and procedure of the police
OL,18,Fand the authorities surrounding this
OL,19,Fcase."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,FHe also wants the Kenyan Police to put
OL,8,Fforward more evidence from their
OL,9,Finvestigation into Kate's killing.
OL,11,FHe said: "We'd really like to see more
OL,12,FCCTV footage from the hotel on the
OL,13,Fnight that it happened, but the other
OL,14,Fday, when we were in court, the police
OL,15,Fsent a guy who brought 36 numbered
OL,16,Fstill photographs that had been ripped
OL,17,Ffrom the CCTV and that was all the
OL,18,Fevidence we could get, which is very
OL,19,Ffrustrating.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,F"They have her two laptops and two
OL,8,Fphones, and apart from its value as
OL,9,Fevidence, which hasn't been used
OL,10,Fbecause the digital forensics team
OL,11,Fapparently haven't been able to access
OL,12,Fthem because they're protected with
OL,13,Fpasswords, which seems unlikely.
OL,15,F"They contain the records of the last
OL,16,Fthree or four years of my sister's
OL,17,Flife, which for me and my Mam would
OL,18,Fbe, you know, priceless."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780419954
OL,3,CBrother of murdered BBC worker
OL,4,Cfrustrated by 'obstructive' Kenyan
OL,5,Cinquest delays
OL,7,FAn Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,8,FDevelopment Office spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"We are providing support to the
OL,10,Ffamily of a British national who has
OL,11,Fdied in Kenya and are in contact with
OL,12,Fthe local authorities."
OL,14,FITV News requested statements from the
OL,15,FKenyan Judiciary, Kenyan High
OL,16,FCommission, and Kibera Courts in
OL,17,FNairobi and awaits a response.
OL,19,FThe inquest, which opened in November
OL,20,F2025 at Kibera Law Courts, resumes on
OL,21,F28 July.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
